      <section eId="sec_319">
        <num>319</num>
        <heading>Penalties</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_319__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>if he was the operator and not the\nowner of the motor vehicle, had no knowledge that the financial security\nrequired for such motor vehicle was not in effect; or</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_319__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>if he was the\nowner and not the operator of the motor vehicle, that he did not permit,\neither expressly or impliedly, the operation of such motor vehicle.\n  5. The civil penalty for a violation of subdivision one of this\nsection shall be seven hundred fifty dollars.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
